<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Brunn, Bischof von Würzburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Peter Rieter, Bürger zu Nürnberg, Hans von Egloffstein zu Mühlhausen bis Walpurgistag sichert und in der Zwischenzeit zum Adressaten kommen wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_403" id="200v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_403_r2l8"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_403_r2l9"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat wıe <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vom </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l10"><expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Mülhawſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / dıe ſıcherheıt . dıe Jm <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Peter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l11"><expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒugeſagt vnd wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒuge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l12">ſchrıben haben / nıht genüglıch dunke etc das haben wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l13">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd haben mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Peter <expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan> dauon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l14">geredt / Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / Daʒ er dıe ſache vnge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l15">uerlıch gemeynt habe / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> / ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l16"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu eren <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jm geredt / daʒ er vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l17"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> hat / daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> hanns von <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> ſıcher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l18">vor Jm ſeın ſülle vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_403_line_1577281991566_5637">Jm </ab></add> keins argen <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> welle noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l19"><expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Oſtern </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l20">
<add><ab facs="#facs_403_r1l1">ſand <expan>walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan> tag </ab></add> ſchıeriſt . Jn <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt meynt der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan> . ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l21">der ſache ʒu <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>rıchten</expan> / daʒ eẅr gnade <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l22">er hofft daʒ Jm vngütlıch geſchehe . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_line_1577282005607_5657"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_403_r2l26"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_403" id="200v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                                                  <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie
                                                  <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> vom
                                                  <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Mülhaws<ex>en</ex></expan> die sicherheit,
                                                die im <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Peter
                                                  <expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan> zugesagt und wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zugeschriben haben,
                                                niht genüglich dunke etc., das haben wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben mit
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Peter
                                                  <expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan> davon geredt; der
                                                hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz er
                                                die sache ungeverlich gemeynt habe. Wie
                                                  <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu eren
                                                  <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit im geredt,
                                                daz er uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> hat,
                                                daz der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Hanns von
                                                  <expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> sicher vor im
                                                sein sülle und <add>im</add> keins argen
                                                  <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> welle noch
                                                  <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> von
                                                  <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><add>sand <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                            tag </add>
                                            schierist</q>01.05.1422</note></app>; in
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit meynt der
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Ryet<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> der sache zu
                                                  <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>richten</expan>, daz ewr
                                                gnade <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, als er hofft, daz im
                                                ungütlich geschehe. Denn wo wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                                                wolgefallen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
